title: The Cantonal Court in Sarajevo refuses to order detention for tram driver Adnan Kasapović
description: SARAJEVO, February 15 (FENA) – The Cantonal Court in Sarajevo rejected the request to place Adnan Kasapović, the tram driver whose tram derailed near the National Museum of Bosnia and Herzegovina, in pre-trial detention. The accident resulted in the death of Erdoan Morankić and left four other people injured.
